  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. A 30% decrease means multiplying by 1 &minus; 0.30 = 0.7 per unit increase in <i>x</i>. With initial value <i>r</i>(0) = 22, the function is <i>r</i>(<i>x</i>) = 22(0.7)<sup><i>x</i></sup>.</p>",
